'''Sonic nullifiers''' were an example of high-tech ear protection. They made use of counterwave-nullifiers, an innovation that was pioneered by [[Shipyard/Legends|shipyard]] workers. They provided adequate protection against attacks from [[Sonic blaster/Legends|sonic blasters]] and other forms of auditory attacks.

